  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 43-13-121, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO DIRECT THE DIVISION OF MEDICAID TO APPLY FOR NECESSARY WAIVERS AND EXPEND FUNDS APPROPRIATED AS NECESSARY TO PROVIDE HOME- AND COMMUNITY-BASED SERVICES TO PERSONS WHO ARE AGED/DISABLED, PHYSICALLY DISABLED OR RECIPIENTS WITH TRAUMATIC BRAIN INJURY/SPINAL CORD INJURY, TO ELIMINATE ANY WAITING PERIOD FOR SERVICES; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
